title: Sexual Abuse History, Rape Fantasies, and Saudi Women
description:
Dr. Kirk Honda talks about if sexual abuse history makes one a bad partner, male rape fantasies, and the plight of a Saudi woman.

The Psychology In Seattle Podcast.

Aug 1, 2018.
